CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

August 29, 2006

[Cite as 08/29/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-4433.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-0447. State ex rel. Westhoven v. Yost.

Franklin App. No. 05AP-179, 2006-Ohio-211. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
